OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784906303
OL,3,CCoroner finds ambulance delays
OL,4,Ccontributed to death of man
OL,6,FA coroner has ruled a delay in getting
OL,7,Fan ambulance to a County Durham man
OL,8,Fwho was suffering a medical emergency
OL,9,Fcontributed to his death.
OL,11,FAndrew Watson, who was 32, died in
OL,12,FOctober 2019 at his supported living
OL,13,Fcomplex Cecil Court in Langley Moor.
OL,15,FHe had suffered respiratory failure
OL,16,Fcaused by airway obstruction from
OL,17,Fquinsy, a rare complication of
OL,18,Ftonsillitis.
OL,20,FAndrew first called 999 at 5.38pm on
OL,21,Fthe evening of 10 October 2019.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
