FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784906303
OL,3,CCoroner finds ambulance delays
OL,4,Ccontributed to death of man
OL,6,FBased on the symptoms Andrew described
OL,7,Fin a further 999 call shortly before
OL,8,F6.30pm, an independent expert witness
OL,9,Ftold the coroner's inquest that
OL,10,FAndrew's condition did not become
OL,11,Fcritically life threatening until
OL,12,F6.35pm.
OL,14,FThe witness said if Andrew had arrived
OL,15,Fat hospital before 6.35pm, an
OL,16,Femergency procedure could have been
OL,17,Fcarried out which would likely have
OL,18,Fsaved his life.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784906303
OL,3,CCoroner finds ambulance delays
OL,4,Ccontributed to death of man
OL,6,FHowever, an ambulance did not arrive
OL,7,Fat Andrew's accommodation until
OL,8,F6.45pm, by which point, according to
OL,9,Fthe inquest report, Andrew's medical
OL,10,Fcondition had "ceased to be
OL,11,Fsurvivable".
OL,13,FThe ambulance arrival time was over an
OL,14,Fhour after Andrew's first 999 call,
OL,15,Fdespite his case being prioritised as
OL,16,Fcategory 2, which has a target
OL,17,Fresponse time of 18 minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784906303
OL,3,CCoroner finds ambulance delays
OL,4,Ccontributed to death of man
OL,6,FIn his inquest report, the coroner
OL,7,Fwrote: "Had ambulances been more
OL,8,Freadily available, Andrew probably
OL,9,Fwould have survived. In effect,
OL,10,Fservice delays contributed to his
OL,11,Fdeath."
OL,13,FThe coroner has recorded the cause of
OL,14,FAndrew's death as "natural death to
OL,15,Fwhich the delayed arrival of an
OL,16,Fambulance contributed".
OL,26,@vD@SOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
