OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784906303
OL,3,CCoroner finds ambulance delays
OL,4,Ccontributed to death of man
OL,6,FIn a statement following the
OL,7,Fconclusion of the coroner's inquest,
OL,8,FKaren O'Brien, Deputy Chief Executive
OL,9,Fat North East Ambulance Service, said:
OL,10,F"We are truly sorry for Andrew's death
OL,11,Fand the distress caused to his family.
OL,13,F"We did not respond as quickly as we
OL,14,Fshould have when he called us, and we
OL,15,Fhave always acknowledged that this
OL,16,Fdelay likely contributed to his death.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784906303
OL,3,CCoroner finds ambulance delays
OL,4,Ccontributed to death of man
OL,6,F"We have taken significant steps since
OL,7,F2019 to reduce the delays to ambulance
OL,8,Fresponses, which has included
OL,9,Fsubstantial investment in more
OL,10,Fparamedics and more ambulances.
OL,12,F"Today, our service is performing more
OL,13,Fstrongly and reaching people faster."
OL,15,FAndrew's mother Liz Watson said she
OL,16,Fhopes the lessons identified through
OL,17,Fthe inquest, along with the changes
OL,18,Fthe ambulance service says it has
OL,19,Fmade, mean others facing a medical
OL,20,Femergency receive the care they need
OL,21,Fin time.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784906303
OL,3,CCoroner finds ambulance delays
OL,4,Ccontributed to death of man
OL,6,FShe added: "Nothing can bring Andrew
OL,7,Fback. He was only 32 years old and had
OL,8,Fhis whole life ahead of him. He was
OL,9,Ffunny, intelligent, kind and full of
OL,10,Flife. Andrew brought warmth, laughter
OL,11,Fand energy wherever he went. He was
OL,12,Fdeeply loved by his family and
OL,13,Ffriends, and he is missed every single
OL,14,Fday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784906303
OL,3,CCoroner finds ambulance delays
OL,4,Ccontributed to death of man
OL,6,F"We are grateful that the inquest has
OL,7,Ffinally been able to examine what
OL,8,Fhappened and establish the facts
OL,9,Fsurrounding Andrew's death. It has
OL,10,Fbeen acknowledged by North East
OL,11,FAmbulance Service that the delay in
OL,12,Fgetting an ambulance to Andrew
OL,13,Fcontributed to his death.
OL,15,F"We also acknowledge the apology that
OL,16,Fhas now been offered to our family,
OL,17,Fwhich came after many years of
OL,18,Funanswered questions and after we had
OL,19,Fto fight for this inquest to be
OL,20,Freopened."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/8
